uildings survey/historic american engineering record/historic american landscapes survey"], "score": 16.865658, "shelf_id": "HABS SC,45-KING,1-", "site": ["pictures"], "subject": ["houses"], "timestamp": "2025-01-13T21:40:53.842Z", "title": "Nelson House, Kingstree, Williamsburg County, SC", "type": ["still image"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sc0385/"}], "resource": {"fulltext_file": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/scu/batch_scu_flopeye_ver01/data/sn93067841/00295861757/1920111801/0336.xml&format=alto_xml&full_text=1", "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:scu:batch_scu_flopeye_ver01:data:sn93067841:00295861757:1920111801:0331/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg", "pdf": "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/ndnp/scu/batch_scu_flopeye_ver01/data/sn93067841/00295861757/1920111801/0336.pdf", "segment_count": 12, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn93067841/1920-11-18/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}, "resources": [{"fulltext_file": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/scu/batch_scu_flopeye_ver01/data/sn93067841/00295861757/1920111801/0336.xml&format=alto_xml&full_text=1", "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:scu:batch_scu_flopeye_ver01:data:sn93067841:00295861757:1920111801:0331/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg", "pdf": "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/ndnp/scu/batch_scu_flopeye_ver01/data/sn93067841/00295861757/1920111801/0336.pdf", "segment_count": 12, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn93067841/1920-11-18/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "segment_id": "/service/ndnp/scu/batch_scu_flopeye_ver01/data/sn93067841/00295861757/1920111801/0336.xml", "segments": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn93067841/1920-11-18/ed-1/?sp=6"], "batch": ["scu_flopeye_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "composite_location": ["0/united states/", "1/united states/south carolina/", "2/united states/south carolina/williamsburg/", "3/united states/south carolina/williamsburg/kingstree/"], "contributor": ["university of south carolina; columbia, sc"], "date": "1920-11-18", "dates": ["1920-11-18"], "description": ["Hp Hmrnty iiirrurii W F Tolley L H Cromer Jr Publishers THURSDAY NOVEMBER 18 1920 KINGSTREE NEEDS A HOTEL At present Kingstree has no hotel The boarding houses of Kingstree are doing all they can to take care of our transient guests who find upon arrival here that Kingstree affords NO hotel accommodations What about the old Kellahan Hotel We are reliably informed that the board of directors of the corporation that recently purchased this property have decided to hold it Hold it for what The former owner held it and could have continued to hold it but he doubtless said to himself Whats the use Kingstree needs a hotel I dont want to bother with it and Ill just sell it to someone who willand r i 41 n give xuiitrec a iiutci mat v 111 ki the traveling public modern hotel accommodations Well he did sell and sold out cheap Kinstreee needs a hotel and the only thing to do is for the board of directors of the new project to get busy and give Kingstree a hotel Procrastination is the thief of time Time is money and money is hard to get now we are told but"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2024-01-24T14:39:53.397Z", "group": ["ndnp/scu", "university-of-south-carolina-columbia-sc-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn93067841/1920-11-18/ed-1/?sp=6", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:scu:batch_scu_flopeye_ver01:data:sn93067841:00295861757:1920111801:0336/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=270&w=175", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:scu:batch_scu_flopeye_ver01:data:sn93067841:00295861757:1920111801:0336/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=541&w=350", "https://